data.description: This home qualifies for the 3-2-1 buy down program which lowers your interest ask me how?  Welcome to your dream home! This recently renovated two-story gem offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm. Situated on a corner lot, this property boasts numerous features that will make it love at first sight. With four bedrooms, there's plenty of room for your family or guests to enjoy privacy and comfort. Two well-appointed bathrooms ensure convenience, while two kitchens make it ideal for in-law or teen arrangements. The versatile layout, with both interior and exterior staircases, gives you options to rent one floor or create the ultimate family haven. Enjoy the outdoors in style with enclosed porches and a deck, perfect for sipping morning coffee or hosting a BBQ. The spacious yard is ideal for gardening, playtime, or just soaking up the sun, and a three-car garage provides ample space for vehicles and storage. Some newer windows add energy efficiency and aesthetic appeal, while a new furnace and AC keep you comfortable year-round. Original hardwood floors offer timeless beauty underfoot. This home is a rare find, offering character, space, and income potential with separate utilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own! For more information or to schedule a viewing, contact us today.
